    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This ragged piece of white cloth is wrapped around the grip, stock, or haft of the affixed weapon. When you activate the talisman, you gain the effects of a *sanctuary* spell (DC 20) lasting for 1 minute. If you draw the affixed firearm, the effect ends immediately and the talisman crumbles.",
